     Schema     |             Name             | Type  |   Owner    |       Table
----------------+------------------------------+-------+------------+-------------------
{ ... }
 eucalyptus_osg | idx_bucket_tags_bucket_uuid  | index | eucalyptus | bucket_tags
 eucalyptus_osg | idx_bucket_uuid              | index | eucalyptus | bucket_tags
 eucalyptus_osg | idx_cors_bucket_uuid         | index | eucalyptus | cors_rules
 eucalyptus_osg | idx_lifecycle_bucket_uuid    | index | eucalyptus | lifecycle_rules
{ ... }
{noformat}

Seen in cloud-debug.log:

{noformat}
Tue May 17 10:33:01 2016  INFO [Upgrades:main] Registered @PreUpgrade: ObjectStorage => class com.eucalyptus.objectstorage.upgrade.\
DropConflictingBucketIndex
{noformat}

I see no mention of this index being dropped in my {{postgresql-Tue.log}} .
